## Custom Modes (Optional)

Rules cannot influence Auto model selection. For task-based model/behavior switching: Cursor Settings > Chat > Custom Modes. Create modes (e.g., Debug, Architecture) with model preselection and custom instructions. Invoke via mode dropdown.

